{"tid":1198180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"團結！團結！團結！","createTime":"2019-06-10T07:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T08:26:31.000Z","uid":93479,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ce9207bd1ec88d1b7a9409b7ec70a3c18632e6","tid":1198180,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"和理非同勇武係一天一地，但大家共同敵人係港共！！<br />\n<br />\n大家請拋低成見，唔好掛住內耗踢人捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n和理非非做後勤支援，靜坐堵塞黑警支援出入口，幫手運送物資，幫手治療前線勇士<br />\n勇武就衝，打游擊，搞破壞，衝據點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唯有團結就事成！！我哋只有一個身份<br />\n<br />\n就係  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人</strong></span>"},{"pid":"c9bfe2fa8c63a54f421b909a7ad94230ec635edc","tid":1198180,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e464467483d10e44e7764cf6eadbc08fdfba79f","tid":1198180,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T08:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}